snippet.title: Rugby 2004 - PS2 Gameplay (4K60fps)
snippet.description:
Rugby 2004 - PlayStation 2 Gameplay (4K60fps).

Rugby 2004 is an installment of Electronic Arts' Rugby video game series. The game was developed by HB Studios, published by EA Sports, and released in 2003 for Microsoft Windows and PlayStation 2.
